<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Alex. Brown on Electronic Arts.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Alex. Brown on Electronic Arts.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Alex. Brown analyst Larry Marcus said he has a posiitve outlook for Electronic Arts Inc.</p>
<p>-- raised rating to strong buy from buy.</p>
<p>-- said company has strong products in the pipeline.</p>
<p>-- expects that Christmas this year &quot;will be one of the healthiest video game environments in years.&quot;</p>
<p>-- maintained earnings estimate of $1.30 per share for the 1998 year, ending next March.</p>
<p>-- shares jumped 1-7/8 to 30-7/8.</p>
</text>
